title: 4 Questions to Find Your Purpose

description:
Episode 576 - Wouldn't it be great if your passion was also your job? Then your job would literally be waking up, doing what you love and being paid for it. Well it is 100% possible, you just need to learn the secret Japanese technique to finding your passion. In this episode, I will teach you the secret to finding your passion and making money off of it.   If you want to join Tony Robbins free webinar on how to start a successful online company go to 2019tony.com
